tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE ar_brand_experiences (
    experience_id INT,
    user_id INT,
    brand_name VARCHAR(255),
    rating INT,
    feedback TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE user_interactions (
    interaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
    interaction_date TIMESTAMP,
    interaction_details TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE brand_experiences (
    experience_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    experience_type VARCHAR(50),
    experience_date TIMESTAMP,
    experience_details TEXT
);
